            <title>[ZOOKEEPER-1984] testLeaderTimesoutOnNewQuorum is a flakey test </title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/ZOOKEEPER-1984</link>
                <project id="12310801" key="ZOOKEEPER">ZooKeeper</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;I&apos;m seeing intermittent failures in testLeaderTimesoutOnNewQuorum&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt; It&apos;s failing both on jdk6 and jdk7. (this is my personal&lt;br/&gt;
jenkins, I haven&apos;t see any other failures than this during the past&lt;br/&gt;
few days).&lt;/p&gt;

